    <string name="card_match_instruction">Match pairs of identical fruits! You have 60 seconds to collect as many stars as possible – completing a level gives you extra time.\n\nHow to play:\n• Memorize the card layout for 2 seconds before they flip.\n• Tap cards to reveal them.\n• Matching pairs stay on the board; non-matching pairs flip back after a moment.\n\nBonuses:\n• Earn stars for each matched pair.\n• Completing a level adds 10 seconds and moves you to the next board.</string>
    <string name="number_addition_instruction">Find numbers that add up to the target sum! You have 60 seconds to earn as many stars as possible.\n\nHow to play:\n• Select 2 (or 3 on higher levels) numbers from the grid.\n• Their sum must match the target number.\n• Correct sums remove the numbers from the board; incorrect sums flash red.\n\nBonuses:\n• Earn stars for each correct sum.\n• Completing a level moves you to a harder level with a larger grid.</string>
